{"filter":false,"title":"epl.1.php","tooltip":"/events/epl.1.php","undoManager":{"mark":36,"position":36,"stack":[[{"start":{"row":57,"column":10},"end":{"row":64,"column":15},"action":"remove","lines":[" <p class=\"methodText\"><strong>September 13th, 2014 - Miracle City, IND : </strong>As the 20 Years Celebrations heated up at Miracle, the first event that kicked off in the season is our very own Employee Premier League, a cricket tournament organized for the employees at our Offshore Development Center to showcase their talents on the field. ","          </p>","          <p class=\"methodText\">The tournament kicked off on September 13th and ended up in the last week of October, which lead to our ultimate champion. It was really a beautiful challenge between the Miracle City Sr. Development Team and the SAP Development Team, with the SAP Development folks reaching out for ultimate glory. They were titled the eventual champions with their fiery brave performance etching a awesome image in everybody's minds.","          </p>","          <p class=\"methodText\">Nagendra Kumar Eleswarapu believes SAP team of Miracle Heights have built a strong squad who are capable of winning Employee Premier League title this year. The day belonged to the opponent batsmen who were in a mood to punish the spinners yet played equally good knock against the pacers including a blistering hook shot. Vinay Kumar Bommana played a career defining innings as his magnificent batting propelled a tough game against SAP team in the semi finals of Employee Premier League.","          </p>","          <p class=\"methodText\">The 20 years celebrations for Team Miracle are set to kick into full swing in the month of December with a lot of fun activities set to kick in.","          </p> "],"id":2},{"start":{"row":57,"column":10},"end":{"row":66,"column":15},"action":"insert","lines":["<p class=\"methodText\">International Women’s Day is the day on which we express gratitude to women who have fought and broken all the barriers to reach the pinnacle of success in every sphere of life. This day is very special to them all around the globe.","            </p>","          <p class=\"methodText\">To grace this memorable day, Team Miracle had arranged a special dinner for the ladies at our offshore facilities Miracle-City cafeteria and Miracle-Heights lawn besides really fun filled activities. Also, the team wished them with beautiful quotes on specially designed greeting cards.","             </p>","         <p class=\"methodText\">It was their time and all the women had gathered for the event. It started with fun activities like Treasure Hunt, Ramp Walk, Dubsmash, Memory Game and it went on with great fun. The lights were on and the DJ was up! Girls couldn’t resist the pumping beats as their power-packed energy rocked the dance floor.","         </p>","         <p class=\"methodText\">Strengthening women in IT as the motive, women from Miracle, in white T-shirts, walked all the way from YMCA to RK beach early in the morning at 07:00 AM on March 11, 2017. They were very proud and felt honoured to be a part of this great unity walk.","         </p>","         <p class=\"methodText\">Finally, women of Miracle were rejoiced with all the fun and activities held at the event and felt special for being their kind. Miracle had a great time recognising the power of women and took immense joy in wishing a happy International Women’s Day!","           </p>"]}],[{"start":{"row":67,"column":8},"end":{"row":78,"column":14},"action":"insert","lines":["<div class=\"row\">","       <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","      ","      <img src=\"../images/events/womens-day2-2017.png\" alt=\"womens-day\" class=\"img-responsive\"></img>","      ","        </div>","        <div class=\"col-sm-6\">","      ","      <img src=\"../images/events/womens-day3-2017.png\" alt=\"womens-day\" class=\"img-responsive\"></img>","      ","        </div>","        </div>"],"id":3}],[{"start":{"row":46,"column":3